2026-06-15
- Added Qingguo-compatible proxy API parsing for JSON `data[].server` responses while preserving legacy text `ip:port` support.
- Exposed proxy extraction throttling and Qingguo proxy authentication environment variables for local and Docker runs.
- Prevented blocked EastMoney Guba list HTML from being parsed after anti-bot detection.
- Switched Guba list pagination to the mobile WebArticleList API before falling back to desktop HTML parsing.
- Corrected Guba detail failure metrics so capped-but-unselected URLs are not counted as detail failures.
- Corrected CN/HK media detail failure metrics to avoid double-counting missing detail responses.
- Added final body-text success metrics and used Guba list `post_content` as social content fallback.
- Raised the Yicai media detail cap to improve final media body coverage.
- Made Guba list pagination stop only when a whole page is older than the requested window.
- Added retryable Guba mobile list API page fetches so transient short-lived proxy failures do not terminate older custom-window pagination.
- Replaced real-looking proxy/API secrets in `.env.example` with placeholders and documented `GUBA_LIST_API_MAX_ATTEMPTS`.
- Made Guba list pagination depth configurable with `GUBA_MAX_LIST_PAGES=600` and added a custom-window page seek so high-volume tickers can reach older 7-day windows without scanning from page 1.
- Increased the Guba mobile list API page size to a configurable, tested-stable `GUBA_LIST_PAGE_SIZE=100` to reduce high-volume ticker window pagination cost.
- Included custom-window seek time in the Guba social `list` duration metric and added page-range/page-request fields to the social crawl summary.

2026-06-17
- Improved CN/HK media body capture by expanding detail-fetch coverage, retrying transient detail proxy failures, parsing CLS Next.js article bodies, and using controlled company-name suffix aliases without changing relevance thresholds.
- Added alias-aware yicai and Sina list-item evidence filtering so records with no target ticker/name evidence are dropped before detail fetch and relevance labeling.
